data.value:
DPA Maker is an app I coded in C# in order to make filling out these trivial DPA forms that the government makes us fill out much easier. Seriously though, obesity is a constantly growing problem and Gordon Campbell thinks he can wave his magic wand and cure it with bureaucracy? Anyways, here you go, I spent I long time coding this (It’s 1:39 AM right now) so enjoi!
-Josh Stuible
